{"ts":"2026-04-26T20:17:00.482Z","author":"audit-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"Specific gaps found:\\n1. SDK.md missing: cli-contracts exports inventory (PM_CORE_COMMAND_NAMES, PM_TOOL_ACTIONS, PM_TOOL_PARAMETERS_SCHEMA, withFlagAliasMetadata, toCompletionFlagString, Commander helpers)\\n2. EXTENSION_CAPABILITIES / EXTENSION_CAPABILITY_* not listed in SDK.md\\n3. EXTENSIONS.md: registerCommand + inline flags needs schema capability (not documented)\\n4. EXTENSIONS.md: registerExporter requires importers capability (same as importers) but not stated\\n5. ExtensionCommandArgumentDefinition not exported from SDK but used by CommandDefinition.arguments\\n6. CommandDefinition.handler should have @deprecated JSDoc annotation\\n7. ./cli package.json entry has empty type declarations"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/id","value":"pm-qrxb"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/title","value":"SDK docs: document cli-contracts exports and extension capability requirements"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/description","value":"SDK audit found gaps: (1) docs/SDK.md does not document the large cli-contracts layer (PM_CORE_COMMAND_NAMES, PM_TOOL_ACTIONS, PM_TOOL_PARAMETERS_SCHEMA, flag contracts). (2) docs/EXTENSIONS.md does not note that registerCommand with inline flags requires schema capability, and registerExporter requires importers capability."},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/type","value":"Task"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/tags","value":["documentation","extensions","pm-cli","sdk"]},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/created_at","value":"2026-04-26T20:17:00.482Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/updated_at","value":"2026-04-26T20:17:00.482Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/deadline","value":"2026-05-01T20:17:00.482Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/author","value":"audit-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/fron